Foodie – Food Menu Web App

A simple food ordering/menu web application that allows users to browse different food categories such as breakfast, lunch, and dinner. Users can view food items with descriptions, preparation time, servings, and prices. The project demonstrates basic frontend web development concepts including UI design, responsive layout, and menu display functionality.

Features:
Browse food categories
View food items with price and details
Simple and clean UI
Responsive design

Tech Used:
HTML
CSS
JavaScript
